quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  12,96,jab khushkhabri dainay wala aa pouncha to kurta Yaqoob ke munh par daal diya aur woh Beena ho gay ( aur beiton se ) kehnay lageykiya mein ne tum se nahi kaha tha ke mein khuda ki taraf se woh baatein jaanta hon jo tum nahi jantay
  12,97,beiton ne kaha ke abba hamaray liye hamaray gunah ki mughfirat mangi-ye. be shak hum khatakaar they
  12,98,unhon ne kaha ke mein apne perwar-digaar se tumahray liye bakhshish maanguu ga. be shak woh bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  12,99,jab yeh ( sab log ) Yousuf ke paas puhanche to Yousuf ne apne walidain ko apne paas bithaya aur kaha misar mein daakhil ho jaiye khuda ne chaha to jama khatir se rhiye ga
  12,100,aur apne walidain ko takhat par bithaya aur sab yousuf ke agay sajda mein gir parre aur ( is waqt ) Yousuf ne kaha abba jaan yeh mere is khawab ki tabeer hai jo mein ne pehlay ( bachpan mein ) dekha tha. mere perwar-digaar ne usay sach kar dekhaya aur is ne mujh par ( bohat se ) ahsaan kiye hain ke mujh ko jail khanaay se nikala. aur is ke baad ke shetan ne mujh mein aur mere bhaiyon mein fasaad daal diya tha. aap ko gaon se yahan laya. be shak mera perwar-digaar jo chahta hai tadbeer se karta hai. woh Dana ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  12,101,( jab yeh sab baatein holin to Yousuf ne khuda se dua ki ke ) ae mere perwar-digaar to ne mujh ko hukoomat se behra diya aur khowaboon ki tabeer ka ilm bakhsha. ae asmano aur zameen ke peda karne walay to hi duniya aur akhirat mein mera karsaaz hai. to mujhe ( duniya se ) apni itaat ( ki haalat ) mein اٹھائیو aur ( akhirat mein ) apne naik bundon mein daakhil kejio
  12,102,( ae paighambar ) yeh akhbar ghaib mein se hain jo hum tumhari taraf bhaijtay hain aur jab baradran Yousuf ne apni baat par ittafaqkiya tha aur woh fraib kar rahay they to tum un ke paas to nah they
  12,103,aur bohat se aadmi go tum ( kitni hi ) khwahish karo imaan laane walay nahi hain
